(6676,'ACE1291C5A523D6D85475272FABC3C04',NULL,399,'6285173436424','outgoing','Dear International Admissions Office,\n\nI hope you are doing well.\n\nMy name is Mas T. Al-Mehjez from Gaza, Palestine. I applied for the scholarship opportunity at Alma Ata University through the Ministry of Education and was officially nominated for the scholarship.\n\nI received a preliminary acceptance and completed the interview process. However, I have not received any further updates, and I am also unable to locate the previous email communication regarding my application.\n\nCould you kindly resend the admission information and provide an update on my application status?\n\nRegistration Number: 259831044\n\nThank you for your assistance and understanding.\n\nBest regards,\nMas T. Al-Mehjez','text','Sekretariat Univ Alma Ata','','','2026-06-29 02:29:30','2026-06-29 02:29:30'),
(6677,'ACCEEC9D24204D8A95BB94F65CC7D5CA',NULL,600,'6285173436424','outgoing','Dear International Admissions Office,\n\nI hope you are doing well.\n\nMy name is Mas T. Al-Mehjez from Gaza, Palestine. I applied for the scholarship opportunity at Alma Ata University through the Ministry of Education and was officially nominated for the scholarship.\n\nI received a preliminary acceptance and completed the interview process. However, I have not received any further updates, and I am also unable to locate the previous email communication regarding my application.\n\nCould you kindly resend the admission information and provide an update on my application status?\n\nRegistration Number: 259831044\n\nThank you for your assistance and understanding.\n\nBest regards,\nMas T. Al-Mehjez','text','Sekretariat Univ Alma Ata','','','2026-06-29 02:29:41','2026-06-29 02:29:41'),
